{"tid":1910073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪剩係得我一個覺得台灣物價唔係真係咁低","createTime":"2020-03-04T11:46:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T16:02:11.000Z","uid":140953,"like":7,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"f030343ed5de8d507a558d9709b470eb2a621536","tid":1910073,"uid":140953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T11:46:20.000Z","msg":"每次一講台灣人收入，就總會有好多人講台灣人收入雖然低，但物價更低所以佢地都好有錢<br />\n不過去左幾次台灣...好似都唔係真係覺得台灣物價特別低咋wo...<br />\n<br />\n食餐普通d既飯講緊都要40、50蚊港紙，香港茶記明明都係咁上下價錢<br />\n冇錯，佢地都係有好平既野食，但唔係話真係低到可以做大爺咁款...<br />\n<br />\n日常生活用品方面，大家可以想像到係高度全球化下，好多日常生活用品都係國際牌子<br />\n衫如是...電子野如是...<br />\n台灣好多國際品牌既價錢同香港差不多甚至貴過香港都唔少見<br />\n剩係iphone同電子野都已經貴過香港<br />\n當然..依d唔係生活必須品，亦唔係成日要買<br />\n但當你買下衫買下其他野，咪又係咁上下價錢<br />\n<br />\n住既話，最市中心最方便既一樣係可以好貴<br />\n但當然唔係市中心，係可以又大又平，依d真係香港比唔上<br />\n<br />\n行...坐車係幾平<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總結黎講，台灣d物價老老實實同香港真係差不多，但係人工真係差太遠<br />\n(台灣人收息中位數約$10,000港元，香港人收息中位數約$19,000)<br />\n計哂所有生活洗費(唔計樓)，台灣日常生活開支一定唔止香港一半<br />\n當然計埋樓，你香港同邊度比都係輸，咁冇得計既"},{"pid":"a93ac19fda0f84c6b0a2c3a87d303dd4b0d25fde","tid":1910073,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T11:47:25.000Z","msg":"到底大家撐唔撐港台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1909951\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1909951</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c54476c2cd6662cd64908a0d7c313e50844c5e0e","tid":1910073,"uid":37869,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T11:48:05.000Z","msg":"唔計樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc7d61686d4265d4332d82499bf98c07ef3e92a","tid":1910073,"uid":228143,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T11:48:47.000Z","msg":"屌你去旅行等於香港去中環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔通你會去非景點區咩"},{"pid":"9c68869cdf60164225eb5fd03b9c62eed8d1e222","tid":1910073,"uid":22560,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T11:51:18.000Z","msg":"去過幾次台灣以為自己了解晒全台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c66d8e31d0f2293861659a2865c73ba1246382ed","tid":1910073,"uid":62194,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T11:51:40.000Z","msg":"唔計樓我香港都可以做大爺啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcf109e49de226f4eb2737c787ae500afac56f06","tid":1910073,"uid":227275,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T11:53:19.000Z","msg":"台灣人收入低?<br />\n人地最低工資仲高過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ec69b184bcd193b092d218e8a5ab145dae97def","tid":1910073,"uid":263183,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T11:55:06.000Z","msg":"食餐普通d既飯講緊都要40、50蚊港紙q<br />\n我覺得一般地方唔易揾到咁貴既食店"},{"pid":"324d746efee5ec976473775a8e490345c0155401","tid":1910073,"uid":13936,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T11:58:21.000Z","msg":"食餐普通d既飯講緊都要40、50蚊港紙<br />\n<br />\n見到呢句唔洗睇落去<br />\n樓主ON9"},{"pid":"553c2171a1ef5b1ad461678da589f538320354bf","tid":1910073,"uid":140953,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"9c68869cdf60164225eb5fd03b9c62eed8d1e222","tid":1910073,"uid":22560,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T11:51:18.000Z","msg":"去過幾次台灣以為自己了解晒全台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T11:58:50.000Z","msg":"好過好多香港人住左係香港十幾廿年都唔了解自己住緊既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之香港咩都係最慘"},{"pid":"504e4d4a9cc27657fb897d71bc50c29c46778799","tid":1910073,"uid":2654,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T11:59:35.000Z","msg":"住台灣表示某程度上同意"},{"pid":"344ff980a1a6564d27d9dd336f1e130859873e85","tid":1910073,"uid":140953,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fcf109e49de226f4eb2737c787ae500af